build.xml 
    - Single build maintenance file.
   
src/grammars
    - Contains ANTLR and JBurg grammar files used by JBurg.
   
src/java/jburg/burg
   - Semantic analysis and code generator driver files.

src/java/jburg/emitter
    - Code generator back end files.

src/templates
    - Target-specific string templates. 
   
test/BurmTest
   - Self-verifying test cases.

test/patternmatcher
    - Pattern matcher tests.
   
doc
   - Documentation.
